OL,3,CMan with mobility issues has walking
OL,4,Cstick confiscated at airport
OL,6,FA passenger with mobility issues saw
OL,7,Fhis walking stick confiscated by
OL,8,Fsecurity staff at Guernsey Airport.
OL,10,FRobin Hooper regularly uses one to
OL,11,Fhelp him stay steady on his feet,
OL,12,Fparticularly when travelling from his
OL,13,Fhome in Alderney to Guernsey for
OL,14,Fmedical appointments.
OL,16,FRobin's wife Jill says he has used a
OL,17,Fmetal hiking pole or similar for
OL,18,Fyears, travelling through Guernsey, UK
OL,19,Fand overseas airports without any
OL,20,Fissues.
