OL,3,CMan with mobility issues has walking
OL,4,Cstick confiscated at airport
OL,6,FRobin has since received an apology
OL,7,Fand his stick will be returned.
OL,9,FAirport officials are also working
OL,10,Fwith airlines to make sure the rules
OL,11,Fare better communicated in future.
OL,13,FFor example, a hiking pole like
OL,14,FRobin's is not allowed but a walking
OL,15,Fstick or other metal device without a
OL,16,Fspike can be used.
OL,18,FGuernsey Airport adds: "Security
OL,19,Fregulations are set out by the UK
OL,20,FDepartment for Transport.
