OL,6,F"Compliance with these rules is
OL,7,Fmandatory for all airports in the
OL,8,FBritish Isles and Guernsey Airport has
OL,9,Fno discretion in this matter.
OL,11,F"However, airlines will arrange
OL,12,Fassistance for any passengers that
OL,13,Frequire help due to mobility issues."
